title: DRIVE FCA! AT THE 2015 SACRAMENTO AUTO SHOW
text:
DRIVE FCA! AT THE 2015 SACRAMENTO AUTO SHOW Where 
10:00 a.m. Friday, Oct. 16, 2015 Categories 
Events, Sports Drive FCA! at the 2015 Sacramento Auto Show for unique fun with the Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep®, Ram Truck, and FIAT brands! Enter the 2015 $45,000 National Sweepstakes for a chance to win an FCA US vehicle from any one of the Chrysler, Dodge, Jeep, Ram Truck, FIAT or Alfa Romeo brands. Drive FCA! – Register at the tent located on west side of Building B to test drive the latest from Fiat Chrysler Automobiles US including the all-new 2015 Jeep Renegade, a small sport-utility vehicle that offers a unique combination of best-in-class off-road capability, open air freedom and a segment-first nine-speed automatic transmission that contributes to outstanding driving dynamics on and off-road, as well as two fuel-efficient engines, and innovative safety and technology. Available vehicles include: 2015 Chrysler 200, 2015 Chrysler 300, 2015 Chrysler Town & Country, 2016 Jeep Cherokee, 2015 Jeep Grand Cherokee, 2015 Jeep Renegade, 2015 Dodge Challenger, 2015 Dodge Dart, 2015 Dodge Durango, 2015 Ram 1500, 2016 Fiat F00X & 2015 Fiat 500e Drive FCA! Hours of Operation: Friday, October 16 10:00 a.m. – 6:30 p.m. Saturday, October 17 10:00 a.m. – 6:30 p.m. Sunday, October 18 10:00 a.m. – 6:00 p.m. For product information and more visit www.FCANorthAmerica.com.
